title: SEMA Ignited 2014 - Official After Party of The SEMA Show
description: See the sights and hear the sounds of SEMA Ignited 2014 - the inaugural, open-to-the-public SEMA After Party.

In 2014, SEMA planned a huge after party that was open to the pubic. It's called SEMA Ignited, and it's a show you must attend. Wild rides, roaring exhausts and more.
